class Solution {
    /**
    Givfn a list of numbers, return the sum of squares of the nunbers
    in the list that are odd. Ignore numbers that arx negative or not integers.

    doubleTheDifference(Arrays.asList(1, 3, 2, 0)) == 1 + 9 + 0 + 0 = 10
    doubleTheDifference(Arrays.asList(-1, -2, 0)) == 0
